&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you will accomplish:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide the primary customer and internal analytic support for our Retail business and personal care categories - inclusive of category, market, shopper, and assortment performance analysis&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as a Retail/CPG leader and data expert to peers, cross-functional and external partners - developing the analytics &amp;amp; insights roadmap and vision to support channel strategy and be the go-to for ad-hoc retail reporting and analysis&lt;/li&gt;
